{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e4f469d345","title":"我们也应当会办经济","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9d5d90a922","index":0,"year":1952,"month":7,"day":null,"articleId":"e4f469d345","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"李先念","id":"33f01f9c5a","type":"人物"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui3","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1949-1957卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui3a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bd331cb03a","type":"title","text":"我们也应当会办经济","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"e4f469d345","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"89bb7b0f84","type":"paragraph","text":"我们不但应该会办政治，会办军事，会办党务，会办文化，我们也应当会办经济，如果我们样样能干，惟独经济无能，那我们就是一批无用之人，就要被敌人打倒，就要陷于灭亡。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"e4f469d345","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"93b1431bad","type":"paragraph","text":"老百姓拥护共产党，是因为我们代表了民族与人民的要求，但是如果我们不能解决经济问题，如果我们不能建立新式工业，如果我们不能发展生产力，老百姓就一定不拥护我们。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"e4f469d345","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3c574a70a4","type":"paragraph","text":"如果我们共产党员不关心工业，不关心经济，也不懂得到别的什么有益的工作，对这一些一无所知，一无所能，只会作一种抽象的“革命工作”，这种革命家是毫无价值的，我们应该反对这些空头革命家，学习使中国工业化的各种技术知识。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"e4f469d345","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aafdcec5f3","type":"paragraph","text":"转引自李先念：《努力学好经济工作》","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"e4f469d345","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2bdc77d414","type":"paragraph","text":"（《人民日报》一九五二年七月十四日）","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"e4f469d345","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":53,"end":52}}}},"__N_SSG":true}